  "transcript": "I have extensive experience in molecular biology, specifically CRISPR gene editing. In my previous role at GenTech, I led a team that developed a novel delivery system for Cas9 using adeno‑associated viruses. We achieved a 70 percent editing efficiency in primary neuronal cells, which was a significant improvement over the existing methods. Um, I also have hands‑on experience with quantitative PCR to validate edits, and I routinely use Python for data analysis and visualization. Additionally, I presented our findings at two international conferences and authored a first‑author paper in Nature Biotechnology.",
